<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">#Create a checkp[oint]
#For a checkpoint you have to create a copy of the data frame in the state that is now
</span><span class="n">df_reason_mod</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">copy</span><span class="p">()</span>
