<h1 id="extract-the-month-value">Extract the Month value</h1>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">df_reason_mod</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'Date'</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

